Subject: Error message during database creation
Description:
Hello team,

I contact you because during the PingCastle Pro installation, I got an error "26201".

I attach you a screenshot in this ticket and also the SQL database version.
Solution_Comment__c:
Symptoms:
The installer for PingCastle Pro not throwing an error 2206.

Cause:
The user was attempting to install PingCastle with an incorrect version of dotnet.

Resolution:
Installing the correct version of dotnet resolved the issue.
